sequenceDiagram
    autonumber
    participant A as 管理员
    participant F as 前端
    participant S as API服务
    participant UDB as 用户库
    participant LOG as 日志库

    A->>F: 选择用户，点击"冻结"
    F->>F: 弹出冻结原因选择框
    A->>F: 选择原因(content_violation等)

    F->>S: POST /admin/users/{userId}/freeze<br/>{reasonCode: "content_violation"}
    S->>UDB: 开启事务
    S->>UDB: UPDATE user SET<br/>status='frozen',<br/>frozen_time=NOW(),<br/>frozen_reason='content_violation'
    UDB-->>S: 更新成功

    S->>LOG: INSERT operation_log<br/>{action: 'freeze_user', details}
    LOG-->>S: 记录成功

    S->>UDB: 提交事务
    UDB-->>S: 提交成功
    S-->>F: {code: 200, data: {freezeTime, reasonCode, reasonText}}
    F->>A: 展示"冻结成功"
    F->>F: 刷新用户列表
